    public final class SlidePersistAtom
extends RecordAtom
    A SlidePersist Atom (type 1011). Holds information on the text of a given slide, which are stored in the same SlideListWithText(SlidePersistist Atom（类型1011）。保存有关给定幻灯片文本的信息，这些信息存储在同一SlideListWith文本中)
